<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Schedule a Meeting with Your Assigned Agent</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    a{
      color: #3498db
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #3498db;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Schedule a Meeting with Your Assigned Agent</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello  <%= user %>,</p>
      <p>We are pleased to inform you that we have assigned an agent to assist you. To schedule a meeting and discuss your requirements, please use the following link:</p>
      <p><a href="<%= link %>">Schedule Meeting</a></p>
      <p>Feel free to choose a time that works best for you. If you encounter any issues or have specific preferences, please reply to this email, and our team will assist you promptly.</p>
      <p>We look forward to connecting with you!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The Batelian Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
